				\begin{document}$$\frac{\Delta Cost}{\Delta Effect}=\frac{Cost\, CRI-Cost\, RDI}{Survival \,CRI-Survival \,RDI.}$$\end{document}ΔCostΔEffect=CostCRI-CostRDISurvivalCRI-SurvivalRDI.
